{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5b52865efc","title":"大字报——不同身份，不同对待","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（一）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编，1957年8月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e371f0334b","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"5b52865efc"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19389b0801","name":"山西医学院学生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1d2c24ff9b","type":"title","text":"大字报——不同身份，不同对待","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b52865efc"},{"id":"10e84f7fa8","type":"authors","text":"山西医学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b52865efc"},{"id":"393ba01c3d","type":"paragraph","text":"党员发言，面部表情多么自然，有说有笑，标榜自己，会嫖会赌，会喝会穿，检查没有，略为谈谈，通过没有，真太简单。团员：我是团员，工作负责，响应国家召唤！就是群众工作比较难办，今后慢慢来改。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b52865efc"},{"id":"333f393b2a","type":"paragraph","text":"组织结论：注意，注意，以后再改。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b52865efc"},{"id":"34b2071370","type":"paragraph","text":"群众：（要说得自己是最坏的一个）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b52865efc"},{"id":"3db9a5216d","type":"paragraph","text":"我是群众，家庭皆是丑态，不求进步，思想落后，今后痛改前非，改头换面，经过严厉批评，才算了结，否则的话皆由组长乱下结论，作为档案，至今想想，还是提心吊胆。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b52865efc"},{"id":"870f1ed6f4","type":"paragraph","text":" 山西医学院  ×××","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b52865efc"}],"page":{"id":"05e9800c8e","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b52865efc","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}